          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>CFPB Constitutional Reform Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Consumer Financial Protection Act of 2010 to revise the leadership structure of the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau (CFPB). Specifically, the bill replaces the CFPB's director and deputy director with a five-person commission. </p>]]></text>
